header_text: You are at the doctor’s office and they ask you if you are having any COVID symptoms. They list headaches as a possible symptom, and that scares you because this is something you've been experiencing. You remember that headaches are common, and you can rest until you feel better.

elements.Text: Does your headache mean that you are likely sick?
